Fixed input data format to Caffe Model. This has been verified with VGG-19 models for various color and black/white image. 
For other models updated function can be used with appropriate parameters.

@niketanpansare Can you please review the change?

Reshape util to convert tensors in NCHW to CNHW format.

@dusenberrymw can you please review this PR? 

cc @bertholdreinwald @niketanpansare

@niketanpansare -
It turns out that I had removed the code to initialize the initial GPU memory budget as part of my large GPU backend redesign (My bad).
It has now been restored in a more appropriate place.

@bertholdreinwald -
It also turns out that Estimates for the GPU are the same as for CP operations. In so far as I can tell, this should work in most cases. I will have to look at the implementations carefully.
